10 REM Largest product in a grid
20 REM 2 lines of DATA fill 1 row
30 DATA 08, 02, 22, 97, 38, 15, 00, 40, 00, 75
40 DATA 04, 05, 07, 78, 52, 12, 50, 77, 91, 08
50 DATA 49, 49, 99, 40, 17, 81, 18, 57, 60, 87
